      <title>最高法院限制 SEC 内部法官审理欺诈案件</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-27/supreme-court-curbs-sec-s-use-of-in-house-judges-in-fraud-cases</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国最高法院限制了美国证券交易委员会向内部法官提出申诉的能力，称当该机构寻求经济处罚时，被告有宪法权利向联邦陪审团陈述案件。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-27/supreme-court-curbs-sec-s-use-of-in-house-judges-in-fraud-cases</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 27 Jun 2024 14:12:27 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>由于 BTG 考虑贷款，OEC 申请破产保护</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-27/oec-said-to-plan-bankruptcy-protection-filing-as-btg-mulls-loan</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，陷入困境的巴西建筑公司 Odebrecht Engenharia e Construcao SA 正在申请破产保护，其 4600 万美元的债券将于 10 月到期，同时正在与 Banco BTG Pactual SA 洽谈贷款事宜。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-27/oec-said-to-plan-bankruptcy-protection-filing-as-btg-mulls-loan</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 27 Jun 2024 13:25:10 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
